reset_clock_exclusivity(25.10)                  reset_clock_exclusivity(25.10)

Name
       reset_clock_exclusivity  -  Allows  to  reset the set_clock_exclusivity
       constraints applied on pins

Syntax
       reset_clock_exclusivity

       [-help]

        <<pin_name>>

       Allows to reset the set_clock_exclusivity constraints applied on pins.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       <<pin_name>>
              Specifies the name of pins  for  which  clock  exclusivity  con-
              straints need to be reset.

Related Information
              * set_clock_exclusivity

